nodes.text: 1. As per nature's plan? Minus the interference of those who place more importance on the right to destroy than that of life that depends wholly on them. 2. The born do not have the ability to dwell inside other people. They would drown or starve to death since the mechanics to achieve this are not in place. Bearing children is the job of women since they are the ones equipped for the job. Responsibility is a choice all must 'endure' with each new adventure in life. Including the results of a pleasant night.
Oh, just come right out and say it, women are subhuman, all they are is wombs. Come on, let's show the true colors of the pro-fetus movement.
